{"tid":1380443,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"前線義士醒少少得唔得","createTime":"2019-07-29T04:25:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T11:27:07.000Z","uid":130406,"like":46,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0795872c31a76bf385fc6d22633b32a1389c27a4","tid":1380443,"uid":130406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:25:44.000Z","msg":"見過發夢好多手足遮頭遮面<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">就係唔撚遮眼</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">至少都帶返幅黑超啦 或者眼罩黐反光膠紙</span></span> <br />\n由其包面豬咀嗰啲 睇撚晒到你係邊撚個啦 發夢我都認到你係我大學同學 咁班狗睇片呢你話<br />\n<br />\n大佬呀 眼係最易認架 由其前事擲嘢嗰啲 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你要由頭包到落腳 帶三套衫去換</span></span><br />\n我跪係度求你唔好送頭 焗啲未焗啲囉<br />\n<br />\n仲有返去要搭地鐵就早/遲一兩個站落車<br />\n再搵暗換晒衫再行路/其他車返去"},{"pid":"33d64b1bfc80efedeff63907d5642660088c1afd","tid":1380443,"uid":130406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:27:37.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"41eaf8bb2ba845bdf88239c6cd330c88d7a03db5","tid":1380443,"uid":130406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:28:16.000Z","msg":"時代革命"},{"pid":"0859af15d98b71f481158c20880b602314ecb3d2","tid":1380443,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:29:27.000Z","msg":"PUSH <br />\n<br />\n大家一齊支持下<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">【眾籌】 已集合超過1000名巴絲感想 香港編年史</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1379634/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"e9370367561708204b7593b69de548498d582e37","tid":1380443,"uid":130406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:31:57.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"cc37e03f8b94eba0f2becf8dc76b30e6ae8e4102","tid":1380443,"uid":130406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T04:34:30.000Z","msg":"時代革命"},{"pid":"af3670f4e6cf